INSTALL_MSG:
This cog requires Tabulate and BeautifulSoup4.
 Type pip3 install tabulate and then type pip3 install Beautifulsoup4 in cmd prompt to install these libraries.
PM me at Redjumpman#2375 on Discord if you have issues.
NAME: Tibia
DESCRIPTION: Displays Tibia item and monster information as well as Server info. Can check the total number of tibia players online.
